<br>
Fricka was not a born leader. Indeed if she was a born anything, she was a born rogue. Her family's, and her people's hardship had toughened both her body and her mind. The maruading abominations from the South had done their best to destroy her homeland and the Northern people. They had succeeded in destroying their crops, had sullied their bloodlines, and had decimated the organized government. But what these invaders did not know was that the Barbarians could also survive as nomads and that a new organization would arise out...of all things...the rogue underground.<br>
<br>
